source.name: Adopted Budget Rollups by Character
source.description: This shows the adopted budgets for all San Francisco Departments for two fiscal years - FY 2010-2011 and FY 2011-2012. It is organized by Organization(Department and Division), Service (Program), Fund, and Type of Revenue or Expenditure (with details: Character, Object and Sub-object).
